title: Bonobo's Foods
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery
description: Natural food store with a vegetarian take-out kitchen inside. The store sells all-vegetarian food items, ethically source. The kitchen menu features items like veggie sandwiches, vegan fish and chips, burgers, organic muffins and baked goods. Much of the menu is available in vegan versions. Has a small counter and stools for seating/eating-in.
